How Can You Use Linux?
Option 1: VirtualBox/VMware (Recommended for beginners)

Run Linux inside Windows
Safe practice environment

Option 2: WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux)

Linux terminal in Windows 10/11
Easy setup

Option 3: Dual Boot

Install both Windows + Linux
Switch by restarting

Option 4: Cloud VM

AWS EC2, Google Cloud
Real server experience


